                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="resource-card">
                        <div class="resource-card-icon" style="background: #ec4899; color: white;">
                            <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>E-commerce & Retail</h3>
                        <p>From marketplaces to D2C brands, these companies are transforming how India shops and sells products.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
